@ Megalomaniac85 and jadink2002

FOR EVERYBODY WITH THE "INSERT KEY-ERROR"

1) Go to the map called "Crack"
2) Cut the first file, not "rld-fi11"
3) Go to Program Files
4) Go to the map "EA Sports"
5) Go to the map "FIFA 11"
6) Go to the map "Game"
7) Paste the file and replace with the other file
8) Launch the pasted file
9) ENJOY!

The torrent works fine, but FIFA 11 the game itself *blows ass.* I have a 1680x1050 screen, but for some shitty reason the picture is squeezed horizontally causing everyone to look skinny and tall, and there are black bars on the sides. On top of that, you can't adjust any video settings whatsoever- not even the resolution. And the graphics for this game are awful. Somehow EA has been making every FIFA game for the PC progressively shittier and uglier. I'm not sure when the best FIFA game was for the PC, I think it might've been 06. The graphics look playstation 2 quality, blurry textures, no AA, no vertex or pixel shading, etc. 

Download this game if you MUST play it, but DO NOT FEEL BAD for EA. This game isn't worth $0.01. Its an insult that they sell it for $50 at best buy.

The only reason I downloaded it is because i have several xbox 360 controllers for my pc, and only FIFA and a few other sports games have multiplayer on one PC- like every console game has.

Need help! How do i fix the controlls?
I'm using the keyboard and and want to play with normal buttons.
A= Lobb
S= Short Pass
D= Shoot
W=Spring
E= Trouch Pass
Space= Change Player
Shift= Dribbling

To change keys, go to Fifa C:\Program Files\EA Sports\FIFA 11\Game\fifasetup\fifaconfig and enter game settings and keybord keys as you like and then press ok.
